flowchart LR
  U[User / Upstream App] --> P[Planner (LLM)
  produces proposed plan]

  P -->|Proposed steps (JSON)| E[Executor / Gatekeeper
  deterministic
  schema + policy enforcement]

  E -->|Validated invocation| T[Tool Adapter]
  T --> S[Downstream Service/API]

  S --> T -->|Structured result| E
  E -->|Tool result / rejection errors| P
  P -->|Final response| U

  E -.->|Audit log
  (plan, validation, calls)| L[(Logs/Traces)]
